02:24:05.743 --> 02:24:07.443
with us throughout the universe,

02:24:07.863 --> 02:24:10.886
throughout dimensions four, five, six,

02:24:10.966 --> 02:24:13.266
seven, and I think even eight eventually.

02:24:14.667 --> 02:24:15.667
God gets to say,

02:24:16.228 --> 02:24:17.849
ain't it fun that we're able to do

02:24:17.888 --> 02:24:18.610
this together?

02:24:19.290 --> 02:24:21.710
And if we actually were to best him

02:24:21.810 --> 02:24:23.252
and the design of the platypus,

02:24:23.832 --> 02:24:26.192
he's going to be ecstatic for us.

02:24:27.213 --> 02:24:27.513
I mean,

02:24:27.853 --> 02:24:31.055
he actually would like to be bested.

02:24:31.094 --> 02:24:32.056
That's what he's telling you.

02:24:32.595 --> 02:24:36.997
Craig, he epitomizes what a father is.

02:24:37.097 --> 02:24:39.238
He is the ultimate, ultimate,

02:24:39.338 --> 02:24:40.860
ultimate Abba.

02:24:40.940 --> 02:24:41.280
Yes.

02:24:42.906 --> 02:24:46.288
You're happier as a father when your child

02:24:46.448 --> 02:24:48.809
exceeds what you've been able to

02:24:48.850 --> 02:24:51.011
accomplish because of everything that

02:24:51.031 --> 02:24:53.233
you've offered them and taught them and

02:24:53.292 --> 02:24:54.113
given to them.

02:24:54.593 --> 02:24:58.596
When a child fails to follow in your

02:24:58.637 --> 02:25:00.218
footsteps and take advantage of what you

02:25:00.257 --> 02:25:01.077
have, it's a heartache.

02:25:01.759 --> 02:25:02.680
But when your child fails,

02:25:03.393 --> 02:25:05.994
takes it the next step and goes beyond

02:25:06.033 --> 02:25:09.853
what you have established in the family

02:25:09.894 --> 02:25:10.314
business,

02:25:10.713 --> 02:25:12.295
there's no greater sense of pride.

02:25:12.975 --> 02:25:15.215
That's why Yahowah so loves Dowd.

02:25:16.376 --> 02:25:17.476
He's the epitome of that.

02:25:18.115 --> 02:25:24.557
He was about the family business.

02:25:24.596 --> 02:25:28.177
Gentlemen, that includes you too, Wookie.

02:25:29.878 --> 02:25:31.519
He's going, that was a long outro.

02:25:31.658 --> 02:25:33.379
Wow, that was a long one, Dad.

02:25:33.519 --> 02:25:36.040
I'll get up.

02:25:36.360 --> 02:25:36.761
Here I am.

02:25:36.820 --> 02:25:37.980
I'm coming over to you now.

02:25:39.141 --> 02:25:40.082
It's been a pleasure.

02:25:40.262 --> 02:25:43.302
Thank you so much for your endurance in

02:25:43.423 --> 02:25:44.904
this long program.

02:25:44.924 --> 02:25:46.504
But that's what God's looking for.

02:25:46.564 --> 02:25:47.745
He's looking for endurance.

02:25:48.184 --> 02:25:51.466
And I'm delighted that we're surrounded

02:25:51.505 --> 02:25:53.506
now by a family that is in it

02:25:53.527 --> 02:25:55.888
for the long haul and is devoted to

02:25:55.968 --> 02:25:56.987
the cause.

02:25:57.048 --> 02:25:58.228
And I thank you all.

02:25:59.084 --> 02:26:01.049
Have a wonderful evening.

02:26:01.069 --> 02:26:01.710
Happy Shabbat.

02:26:02.012 --> 02:26:02.632
Shabbat Shalom.

